	DESCRIPTION
b-login is a simple login form that you can put in every web application.
It require jQuery to work and it use the jQuery ui to set the style.


	HOW TO USE
There's a simple example in the folder Example where you can see how it works.

To make this work you need to change in the b-login-form.js script the line that you see 
commented in the example.
In this line you must insert the right path of the loginCheck.php file.

Then in the php folder you must edit the mysql.php file to check your database properties 
and the loginCheck.php to edit the query of your database user table.